snippet.textDisplay:
So for those that don’t want to pause and decipher the target bio page, this Portuguese guy doesn’t seem to be a Hammond guy at all actually. Quite a petty mission brief. Even more interesting, he and his wife are known con artists(I’m guessing like oceans 11 level lol), which for those of you in the know is a fun little bit of background for our lady coming season 5. Probably wants to make papa proud (I’m looking at you Wattson) but like... wayyy different motive.

So my theory is that we are looking at the very moment when Rev realizes that he is a simulacrum(spelling?) and switches from these kinds of bounty missions, and instead targets down those responsible for his current state, Hammond.

To someone’s point in the comments, his programming I think would indeed make him believe he was human (yes even when he is going shadow mode and getting shot in the face etc. the program would write out a memory where he would logically have handled that situation, as opposed to what actually happened, like his freakin hand piercing a dude’s chest) and once that realization occurs well... Glass shatter.

For those that made it here thanks for indulging my thoughts 😎
snippet.textOriginal:
So for those that don’t want to pause and decipher the target bio page, this Portuguese guy doesn’t seem to be a Hammond guy at all actually.  Quite a petty mission brief.  Even more interesting, he and his wife are known con artists(I’m guessing like oceans 11 level lol), which for those of you in the know is a fun little bit of background for our lady coming season 5.  Probably wants to make papa proud (I’m looking at you Wattson) but like... wayyy different motive.

So my theory is that we are looking at the very moment when Rev realizes that he is a simulacrum(spelling?) and switches from these kinds of bounty missions, and instead targets down those responsible for his current state, Hammond.

To someone’s point in the comments, his programming I think would indeed make him believe he was human (yes even when he is going shadow mode and getting shot in the face etc. the program would write out a memory where he would logically have handled that situation, as opposed to what actually happened, like his freakin hand piercing a dude’s chest) and once that realization occurs well... Glass shatter.

For those that made it here thanks for indulging my thoughts 😎
